{"tid":1686642,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"係British Council 考完Ielts 等成年都未有成績","createTime":"2019-11-01T09:28:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T06:53:42.000Z","uid":78374,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bdf3089d37ad5261e639748d359548f91be4a096","tid":1686642,"uid":78374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:28:57.000Z","msg":"事緣上年12月去考英國文化協會考電腦version ielts<br />\n考完Speaking 之後入電腦室考reading 同 listening<br />\n點知全部電腦都login唔到 等左2個鐘BC先決定擇日再考<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成班人都燥到仆街 有D人仲要特登黎香港考<br />\n仲識左個鬼妹 原來佢前幾日係同一間房考完listening 之後壞機  成績作廢 要全科重考<br />\n同我一齊考果日又壞多次 又要再考過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身BC同我地講都要全科重考 之後打黎話幫我爭取到唔洗重考Speaking<br />\n重考完 就收到BC封email話investigate緊我個成績<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打去BC問 佢地叫我等就OK 快就2星期<br />\n中間都有打去問  次次都係答 佢地做唔到咩野 都係等英國果邊通知 <br />\n等到我都差D唔記得左<br />\n點知等左就黎成年都仲investigate緊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無人都試過咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"711e6099a75cbf0d70ccede01d2c1a9ba9ba1e1e","tid":1686642,"uid":78374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T10:37:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c5818e8d00cd1ae09b5b0bfa67923a1fffa2c2a0","tid":1686642,"uid":78374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T18:14:49.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a80c8b8ed3bf191a42fa72be32e4d11fd700bea","tid":1686642,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T20:55:31.000Z","msg":"會唔會去考多次仲實際<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50a83f6fc4eac092a73f7eea218d950095babc19","tid":1686642,"uid":109262,"like":0,"dislike":0